## Usage Examples

### Example 1: Basic Setup
```bash
# Navigate to project
cd /path/to/project

# Deploy core rules
ainish-coder --rules

# Deploy to Cursor
ainish-coder --cursor

# Add custom commands
ainish-coder --commands cursor
```

### Example 2: Full Security Setup
```bash
# Deploy core rules
ainish-coder --rules

# Add security tiers
ainish-coder --tier 1  # Code security
ainish-coder --tier 2  # Prompt security

# Deploy to multiple tools
ainish-coder --cursor
ainish-coder --copilot
ainish-coder --windsurf

# Add utilities
ainish-coder --critical
ainish-coder --gitignore
```

### Example 3: All Tiers, All Tools
```bash
# One-command tier deployment
ainish-coder --tier all

# Deploy to all tools
ainish-coder --cursor
ainish-coder --windsurf
ainish-coder --cline
ainish-coder --copilot
ainish-coder --continue
ainish-coder --roocode

# Deploy all custom commands
ainish-coder --commands all

# Add all utilities
ainish-coder --critical
ainish-coder --gitignore
ainish-coder --github-actions
ainish-coder --template-agent
ainish-coder --OSAA
```

### Example 4: Specific Directory
```bash
# Deploy to specific directory
ainish-coder --rules ~/my-project
ainish-coder --tier 1 ~/my-project
ainish-coder --cursor ~/my-project
```

