## Notes

- **[DIR]** = Optional target directory (defaults to current directory)
- **{0-4|all}** = Choose tier number 0-4 or "all"
- **{tool}** = Tool name (cursor, roocode, windsurf, cline, continue, gemini-cli, qwen, goose, all)
- All commands support optional target directory as last argument
- Commands are idempotent (safe to run multiple times)
- Files are copied (not symlinked) to ensure tool-specific customization

